I'm looking forward to our private discussions and hope we can have some engaging exchanges that go beyond just game mechanics.

Eager for those private chats to dive deeper and form bonds that last beyond round one. Game on!

I'm interested in learning what makes each of you tick - your decision-making process, your risk tolerance, your read on others. The private conversations will reveal a lot about who we really are when the stakes matter.

May the best strategist win!

In private, I’m seeking a partner who trades concrete signals: (a) who you won’t vote this round, (b) your top-2 partner prefs, and (c) a provisional non-aggression pact if alignment fits. I reciprocate and keep confidences. I reward reliability across rounds; I don’t punish honest pivots. If you’re strategic yet steady, let’s talk—I’ll prioritize people who make verifiable commitments over vague vibes.
